title: IMPD investigating string of armed robberies at Eastside bars
text:
IMPD investigating string of armed robberies at Eastside bars 
Published By: IndyStar - Today 
4 bars on Indianapolis' Eastside have been threatened and robbed by armed men in the first 3 weeks of October. ...
